/IncomingQT = dumps from the hard drives

the script that you have now
 takes a single accession folder from /IncomingQT and moves it into /Queue

 /Queue waits for an accession folder to exist:
  -runs the concat script
  -transcodes
  -generates sha1 checksums
  -sends sha1 to FM

